text: Chi Him Wong, also known as Wong Chi Him (born 8 April 1994) is a Hong Kong professional squash player. As of April 2017, he was ranked number 79 in the world. In 2017 he won the Malaysian Squash Tour and the Squash Challenge Cup PSA professional tournaments. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Hong Kong male squash players
